{
  "text": "Plant material. Arabidopsis thaliana wild type (Col-0) and amidohydrolase single and triple mutants ilr1, iar3 and ilr1ill2iar3 20 plant cultures were as described in [CITATION_1] . ilr1, iar3 and ilr1ill2iar3 seeds were kindly provided by Dr. Bethany Zolman.",
